<br>
In the end, if Islam and &quot;Western&quot; values/democracy can coexist, that's great.  We're about to find out.  If they can't... /bye Islam.  After all, they're the ones who started this by ramming planes into our buildings.  Personally, I don't see why Islam can't moderate itself a little like it already has in so many areas and for so many people.  I'm looking forward to a free, Islamic, democratic Iraq. <p><!--EZCODE IMAGE START--><img src="http://www.visveres.myguilds.com/sigs/caledhon.gif" style="border:0;"/><!--EZCODE IMAGE END--></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#4D4D4D><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub101.ezboard.com/bthetribunaldotorg.showUserPublicProfile?gid=caledhontelrana>Caledhon TelRana</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>I read boards more<br>than I play EQ....</span><br>  Posts: 796<br> <font color=#FFFFFF>(3/10/03 3:14 pm)</font><br>   <a href=http://pub101.ezboard.com/fthetribunaldotorgfrm36.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=448.topic&index=299>Reply</a>   </td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: &quot;Morality is not relative.&quot;</span><hr size=1> <!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>Perhaps you fail to see the hypocrisy in fags being &quot;born that way&quot;... The Bible says they are going to hell, yet they were born that way, so apparently God MADE them gay.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
