<!--EZCODE QUOTE START--><blockquote><strong><em>Quote:</em></strong><hr>This is the equivalent of forcing YOUR morality down another culture's throat as &quot;superior&quot;.  Even after you've just admited that you &quot;may not possess all of the tools or information necessary to make that judgement or have that knowledge&quot;.<hr></blockquote><!--EZCODE QUOTE END--><br>
